data.description: Amazing starter!  Break into real estate or add to your portfolio! Low-maintenance, move-in-ready, great value. Stop wasting money on rent, and instead build equity enjoying your own yard for pet(s), your own garden, and a new deck. Basement storage. 10 minute walk to Multnomah Village/Parks. Good SW portland schools. Seller bought this home in 2006 and rented out 2nd bedrm, did cosmetic fixes, and was able to build equity, rather than pay someone else rent. It has been a successful rental for the last decade. Almost 0% vacancy during that time. Incredible opportunity for the right buyer.
